  "limitations": [
    "The credential is synthetic and the provider is deterministic; an owner-operated real Pi login smoke remains before C0-02 is declared closed.",
    "OAuth refresh mutations in private run state are intentionally discarded. Parallel OAuth runs remain disabled until locked reconciliation or a credential broker is approved.",
    "The container uses bridge networking so Pi can reach the host control plane and a future model provider. This is accidental-damage containment, not a malicious-code boundary or an egress firewall.",
